<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.3">
<l>mītōṭi vāḷeyiṟu miṉṉilaka muṉvilaku muruvi ṉāḷaik</l>
<l>kātōṭu koṭimūkkaṉ ṟuṭaṉaṟutta kaittalattā veṉṟu niṉṟu</l>
<l>tātōṭu vaṇṭalampun taṇcēṟai yemperumāṉ tāḷai yētti</l>
<l>pōtōṭu puṉaltūvum puṇṇiyarē viṇṇavaril polikiṉ ṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The virtuous ones who sprinkle water and blossoms, praising the feet</l>
<l>Of our great lord of cool Cēṟai where wander bees with pollen, always saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“O [lord] whose hand sliced all at once</l>
<l>The ears and crooked nose of the woman whose appearance flashed</l>
<l rend="indent">as [her] sword[-like] fangs, extending over [her lips],</l>
<l>Shown [like] lightning in front [him],” they will prosper among the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
